sequenceDiagram
    participant P as 乘客端 (Vue 3)
    participant API as Spring Boot API
    participant Lock as Redisson 分布式锁
    participant Score as 评分引擎
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant D as 司机端 (Vue 3)
    participant Event as 事件溯源表

    P->>API: 1. 创建订单 + 支付
    API->>DB: 2. 保存订单 (CREATED → PAID)
    API->>API: 3. 触发派单 (findCandidates)

    Note over API,Score: 评分阶段 (静态 + 动态)

    API->>Score: 4. 获取司机评分排序
    Score->>Score: 距离(40%) + 评分(30%) + 空闲(20%) + 惩罚(10%)
    Score->>Score: 动态修正: +/-modifier, 半衰期衰减
    Score-->>API: 排序后的司机列表

    Note over API,Lock: 锁阶段 (二阶分布式锁)

    loop 遍历候选司机
        API->>Lock: 5a. lock("order:dispatch:{orderId}")
        Lock-->>API: 获取成功
        API->>Lock: 5b. tryLock("driver:lock:{driverId}", 500ms)
        alt 获取成功
            Lock-->>API: 获取成功
            API->>DB: 5c. 重读司机状态 (防 ABA)
            DB-->>API: 司机仍可用
            API->>DB: 5d. 分配司机 (ASSIGNED)
            API->>Event: 5e. 记录事件 DISPATCHED
            API->>D: 6. WebSocket 推送接单通知
            API->>Lock: 5f. 释放 order lock
            Note over API,Lock: 派单成功 ✓
        else tryLock 失败
            Lock-->>API: 超时 (司机已被分配)
            Note over API,Lock: 尝试下一位司机
        end
    end

    D->>API: 7. 接单确认 / 拒单
    alt 接单
        API->>DB: 更新状态 (ASSIGNED → ARRIVED)
        API->>Score: 记录接单 (+5 modifier)
        API->>Event: 记录事件 ACCEPTED
        D->>API: 到达 → 开始行程 → 完成
        API->>Event: ARRIVED → IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED
        API->>P: 8. 生成账单 + 推送评价入口
    else 拒单
        API->>Score: 记录拒单 (-10 modifier)
        API->>Event: 记录事件 REJECTED
        Note over API,Lock: 触发重新派单
    end
